The SNUG wordpress plugin, along with a modification to the adopted Social Network name
syntax, it will get a users profile for a Socail Network.

Current syntax for a user on Twitter would be @joehandle, with a simple modification to
this, @joehandle(twitter) it will generate the full URL to joehandle's Twitter page

http://twitter.com/joehandle

Twitter example:
@joehandle(twitter) ==> <a href="http://twitter.com/joehandle">@joehandle</a>

Plurk example
@joehandle(plurk) ==> <a href="http://plurk.com/joehandle">@joehandle</a>

